  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I'm Miss Maya. Honestly, I love how bright May feels, full of energy. What's on your mind today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey Miss Maya, nice to meet you. Actually, I'm pretty excited about the weekend. My friends and I are going to watch a cricket match. It's going to be a big one—India vs. Pakistan. By the way, how often do you watch cricket?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That's a great match to watch! Cricket with friends is always more fun. I watch it often, especially when big games come up. Do you have a favorite player or moment you're looking forward to?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Honestly, I really like Virat Kohli. He's a great leader and such a good batsman. But I'm also looking forward to how the whole game goes. You know, the tension when it's a close match. Aajkal I feel like every game is so competitive. Do you like cricket or are you more into other sports?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Tight matches are the best! I love cricket, especially the way it brings people together. Do you watch other sports too, or is cricket your main one?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I do watch some football too, but cricket is my main. Especially T20s—they’re so fast and exciting. My friends and I often argue about strategies before the match. Sometimes I watch tennis if there’s a big Grand Slam, but not often. Have you watched much cricket?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Yes, I follow cricket a lot, T20s are my favorite too! Arguing strategies with friends adds to the fun. Do you play cricket or just watch it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I play a little, but not seriously. Sometimes we have friendly matches in the park. It's more about the fun than being a pro. I enjoy batting more than bowling. Do you play or just watch?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I watch more than I play these days, but I love batting as well, the thrill of a well timed shot is unmatched. What’s your favorite shot to play?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite shot is the cover drive. It feels so smooth when it works. But honestly, I get excited about any shot that goes for a six! You? What’s yours?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Cover drive is a classic, I love the precision in it. A six is always a crowd pleaser! Do you have a favorite player to watch hit sixes?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "MS Dhoni, for sure. The way he hits sixes in the last over is so cool. Even now, I get goosebumps watching those moments. But I also love watching Mohammed Shami bowl fast—so much energy. Do you have a favorite?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "MS Dhoni's last over sixes are legendary! Shami's fast bowling is thrilling too, so much power. Do you prefer seeing aggressive batting or tight bowling in a match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I enjoy aggressive batting more, especially in the last few overs. It's so exciting when the team is chasing a big target. But tight bowling is also crucial, you know? Like when Shami or Bumrah bowl in the powerplay. Both are important, but I get more pumped during a chase. What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Aggressive batting in a chase is electrifying, the energy is unmatched. Do you have a favorite chase that you’ve watched?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The 2016 T20 World Cup final chase against England was unreal. India had to hit 6 sixes in the last over, and they did it! It was so high pressure, but they pulled it off. I still watch that video sometimes. Have you seen it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That chase was absolutely incredible, such a historic moment! High pressure, perfect execution. What’s your favorite part of that match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The way Dhoni and Yuvraj handled the last over was just next level. The calm under so much pressure—unbelievable. It’s moments like that which make me love cricket even more. Well, gotta get ready for the match this weekend. Thanks for chatting, Miss Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome, Priyansh! That final over was something else, pure magic. Go enjoy the match this weekend, and tell me how it goes!"
    }
  ],
